[[SECTION]]
TITLE: 1. Purpose

[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
Defines local runtime behavior, Python package/runtime layout, runtime_config.json, data roots, AWS Phase-1 deployment, Docker, EC2, ECR, nginx, HTTPS, Route53, SSM secrets, persistent /app/data mount, GitHub Actions CI/CD, single-user/private-instance boundary, and future backend/session/API runtime model.
<<<

[[/SECTION]]

